Create Plan 7 - "Polish & Optimization"
Plan Name: "Final Polish and Performance"
Plan Description:
Add final touches, optimize performance, and ensure responsive design
across all breakpoints.

Tasks:
Task 1: Add Scroll Animations
Add scroll-triggered animations to all sections:
- Use Framer Motion viewport props
- Fade in from bottom
- Staggered children animations
- Keep subtle and smooth

Task 2: Responsive Testing
Review and fix responsive issues:
- Test all breakpoints (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Ensure text sizes scale properly
- Check spacing and padding
- Mobile menu functionality

Task 3: Performance Optimization
Optimize performance:
- Ensure all images use next/image
- Add proper alt tags
- Check bundle size
- Lazy load below-fold content
- Add loading states

Task 4: SEO Metadata
Update app/layout.tsx metadata:
- Comprehensive title and description
- Open Graph tags
- Twitter card tags
- Favicon setup

Task 5: Accessibility Audit
Check accessibility:
- Semantic HTML throughout
- ARIA labels where needed
- Keyboard navigation works
- Focus states visible
- Color contrast meets WCAG standards